				<p>Our major strategy, as a matter of policy, is the best qualified professionals hired from Computer Science and Engineering, Electrical, Electronics and Telecommunication Engineering, Applied Physics, Business Administration, Finance, Accounting and Economics graduates from leading national and international universities. Our human resources are BS-CSE, BS-ETE, MCP, MCSE, MCDBA, MCPBA+I, MBA, PhD, OCP, Cisco certified and Sun-Java Certified.</p>
